<subSubSection id="C37E65015A7F980BFD24FE88EA57FDA1" pageId="8" pageNumber="201" type="reference_group">
<paragraph id="8BDB368A5A7F980BFD24FE88EA76FE3A" blockId="8.[723,1315,299,722]" pageId="8" pageNumber="201">
<emphasis id="B910EA985A7F980BFD24FE88ED6AFEE5" bold="true" box="[723,879,299,328]" pageId="8" pageNumber="201">Taxonomy.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="4C644D095A7F980BFC47FE88EDA8FEC2" authority="Matschie, 1894" authorityName="Matschie" authorityYear="1894" class="Mammalia" family="Chrysochloridae" genus="Chrysochloris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Afrosoricida" pageId="8" pageNumber="201" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="stuhlmanni">Chrysochloris stuhlmanni Matschie, 1894</taxonomicName>
, 
<materialsCitation id="3B0C3CD75A7F980BFC33FEF1EA76FE3A" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3804714316" pageId="8" pageNumber="201">Ukondjo and Kinyawan- ga, Rwenzori region, Uganda.</materialsCitation>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BDB368A5A7F980BFD24FE3FEA57FDA1" blockId="8.[723,1315,299,722]" pageId="8" pageNumber="201">
Additional specimens are needed to clarify subspecific taxonomy of C. 
<taxonomicName id="4C644D095A7F980BFB7FFE67EB19FE48" authorityName="Matschie" authorityYear="1894" box="[1160,1308,452,485]" class="Mammalia" family="Chrysochloridae" genus="Chrysochloris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Afrosoricida" pageId="8" pageNumber="201" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="stuhlmanni">stuhlmanni</taxonomicName>
. Five subspecies recognized.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C37E65015A7F980BFD23FDB0EF72FC3A" pageId="8" pageNumber="201" type="synonymic_list">
<caption id="DF1B66025A7F980BFD23FDB0EF72FC3A" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6624532" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6624532" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6624532/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="201" targetBox="[109,700,304,718]" targetPageId="8">
